}


'==ARV===

User *-- FileHandler
StreamingService *-- FileHandler

Menu *-- Media

Main --> StreamingService

StreamingService *-- Media
StreamingService *-- Menu
StreamingService *-- User


Media <|-- Movie
Media <|-- Series


Movie <|-- Category
Series <|-- Category



